### 1.3 具體範例（保留完整、依使用者偏好調整）

> 注意：範例中所有捕捉到 Exception 的地方均示範記錄後 rethrow 或包裝再 throw；預期的業務錯誤仍以 Result 回傳。

#### 1.3.1 驗證與業務流程（預期錯誤回傳 Result）
```csharp
public Result ValidateOrderRequest(CreateOrderRequest request) {
    var errors = new Dictionary<string,string>();
    if (string.IsNullOrWhiteSpace(request.CustomerId)) errors["customerId"] = "Customer ID is required";
    if (request.Items == null || request.Items.Count==0) errors["items"] = "At least one item is required";
    if (errors.Any()) {
        return Result.Error("BIZ_VALIDATION_MISSING_CUSTOMERID", "Validation failed", details: errors);
    }
    return Result.Success();
}
```

#### 1.3.2 執行寫入並處理 DB 例外（示範：記錄 + 包裝後 rethrow）
```csharp
public async Task<OrderDto> CreateOrderAsync(CreateOrderRequest request) {
    var validation = ValidateOrderRequest(request);
    if (!validation.IsSuccess) return validation;

    try {
        var order = new Order(request.CustomerId, request.Items);
        await _orderRepository.AddAsync(order);
        await _unitOfWork.SaveChangesAsync();
        return Result<OrderDto>.Success(order.ToDto());
    }
    catch (DbUpdateException dbEx) {
        _logger.LogError(dbEx, "DB update failed for order {OrderId}", order?.Id);
        // 保留原始例外於 InnerException，並以系統識別字串標記
        throw new InfrastructureException("SYS_DB_CONN_FAILED", "Database update failed", dbEx);
    }
    catch (Exception ex) {
        _logger.LogCritical(ex, "Unexpected error in CreateOrderAsync");
        throw; // 不回傳 Result：非預期例外需向上層處理
    }
}
```

註：`InfrastructureException` 範例如下：
```csharp
public class InfrastructureException : Exception {
    public string Code { get; }
    public InfrastructureException(string code, string message, Exception inner): base(message, inner) { Code = code; }
}
```

#### 1.3.3 嘗試重試邏輯示例（恢復策略，最終仍 rethrow）
```csharp
int attempts = 0;
while (true) {
  try {
    await _repo.SaveAsync(entity);
    break;
  }
  catch (TransientException tex) when (++attempts < 3) {
    _logger.LogWarning(tex, "Transient failure, retry {attempt}", attempts);
    await Task.Delay(TimeSpan.FromSeconds(2 * attempts));
  }
  catch (Exception ex) {
    _logger.LogError(ex, "Failed to save after {attempts} attempts", attempts);
    throw new InfrastructureException("SYS_DB_PERSISTENCE_FAILED", "Failed to persist entity", ex);
  }
}
```

#### 1.3.4 錯誤做法示例（僅列出，勿使用）
```csharp
// ❌ 禁止：吞例外或空 catch
try { await _repo.SaveAsync(entity); } catch (Exception) { }
```

